channel.title: Live: WA World Athletics Championships
channel.desc: Coverage of the World Athletics Championships continues from Tokyo with the women's 5,000m final, featuring Faith Kipyegon, and concludes with the final of the men's 800m. Emmanuel Wanyonyi is the favourite to add a world title to the Olympic gold he won in 2024, but Great Britain's Max Burgin could be fighting for a place on the podium.
